  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The role of strut in rhinoplasty has been debated for many years and many research has been
      made over this problem but there is no significant data for descision of surgeon, so this
      study was designed to evaluate the effect of columellar strut in tip projection and rotation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In selected case of rhinoplasty use strut randomly and blindly evalute the effect of it in
      tip rotation and projection.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
